data.description: Motivated seller. Needs to Move ASAP. Move-in ready home with a brand new 85'' wall mounted TV and ALL NEW appliances: Washer, Dryer, Refrigerator, and Stove are included. This spacious and beautifully designed 3-bedroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort and updates. Step inside and be greeted by an inviting great room floor plan, featuring ample natural light, large windows with new window coverings, and designer accent paint. The well-appointed kitchen boasts new appliances, a dining nook, and an extended breakfast bar, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a casual meal. The extended primary bedroom is a true retreat, complete with a double vanity bathroom with a soaking tub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet. The two additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for guests or can be used as a home office or hobby room. The backyard is landscaped for easy care with native desert plantings and a covered patio, ideal for outdoor dining or simply enjoying the Arizona sunshine. As part of the 55+ community, residents have access to a wide range of amenities, including a clubhouse, swimming pool, spa, pickleball court, and shuffleboard. Enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as easy access to major highways for commuting.  Schedule your private showing today and start living the sunny weather retirement lifestyle you've always dreamed of!
